Live coverage: Launch of the X-band Defence Communications Satellite-3 aboard the 4th #H3 launch vehicle (H3 F4)

Please join us on our #JAXA Channel!
https://t.co/AsV3C18dBN
* This live broadcast will be available only in Japanese.

Its important to exercise your right to vote  even in space! 

In our latest episode of "Houston We Have a Podcast," we explain how @NASA_Astronauts vote from the @Space_Station: https://t.co/zYPty9Rrkh https://t.co/UDSUOYyN5c

[Press Release]

Launch Time and Launch window of X-band defense communication satellite-3 aboard the 4th H3 Launch Vehicle (H3 F4) [Rescheduled]

This month, Saturn shines in the south most of the night, Jupiter rises in the early evening alongside Taurus and Orion, while Mars trails a couple of hours behind, visible high in the early morning sky. #Skywatching
